Package: libukui-slab0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: beautification app library
 This library provides functionality to create applications like UKUI
 control center and the application-browser from gnome-main-menu.
 .
 This library has been forked from GNOMEv2 by the UKUI project.

Package: libukui-slab-dev
Section: libdevel
