Depends: libukui-slab0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
Description: beautification app library (development headers)
 The libukui-slab library provides functionality to create applications
 like UKUI control center and the application-browser from gnome-main-menu.
 .
 This package contains the development files for libukui-slab.

